data.description: Schedule Your Exclusive and Private Showing Today! Stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom, Plus Media or Office.  This home in a gated community, conveniently situated near major Highway 20 for easy commuting between Orlando and Tampa. This well-designed residence features a split floor plan, offering privacy with the Primary bedroom with an on-suite bath on one side and the remaining bedrooms on the other and the guest suite on a separate side.    One of the bathrooms is a Jack and Jill, adding a touch of luxury and convenience. The open floor plan creates a seamless flow between the living spaces, perfect for entertaining. Enjoy the Florida sunshine in your back patio adorned with pavers, and relish the private and spacious backyard.    The master bath boasts an on-suite garden tub and a separate shower, providing a spa-like retreat within the comfort of your home. The kitchen is a chef's delight, equipped with stainless steel appliances, elegant wood cabinets, and granite countertops, making it a perfect space for culinary adventures.    Additional features include a paver driveway, adding to the home's curb appeal, and stone accents that enhance its aesthetic appeal. With Legoland just a short distance away, and other theme parks centrally located, you'll have endless entertainment options and a Media Room. Plus, the property is less than 8 miles from Legoland, ensuring fun-filled weekends for the whole family.    Experience the best of Florida living in this centrally located, beautifully appointed home with all the modern amenities you desire. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home!
